WorkflowInfo.Details: This process escalates an incident and waits for a response from someone in the escalation list. In case no one responded, an email is sent to inform no one is handling the problem. In case there was a response the workflow follows up with the person who took ownership every minute, and closes the incident when it is reported as solved.
